OL,6,FCouncillors in are set to approve the
OL,7,Flargest budget cut in local authority
OL,8,Fhistory - including a 21% increase in
OL,9,Fcouncil tax over two years, in return
OL,10,Ffor fewer services.
OL,12,FIn an interview with ITV News
OL,13,FCentral's main presenter, Sameena Ali-
OL,14,FKhan, the leader of said the cuts are
OL,15,Fsomething he "never envisaged or
OL,16,Fwanted to bring to the council".
