OL,3,CCouncil leader says #300m Birmingham
OL,4,Cbudget cuts are 'really tough decision'
OL,6,FThe plan to be voted on tonight will
OL,7,Fsee #150million cut this year and the
OL,8,Fyear after - made up of #51m from
OL,9,Fchildren services and #23m from adult
OL,10,Fsocial care.
OL,12,FRoad maintenance will be cut by
OL,13,F#12million and fortnightly bin
OL,14,Fcollections from 2025 will save
OL,15,F#4.5million.
OL,17,FAll that while council tax is hiked by
OL,18,F10% this year and 10% the year after.
