OL,7,FBirmingham City Council told ITV News
OL,8,FCentral: "I've been really clear that
OL,9,Fthere's issues we need to take
OL,10,Fresponsibility for here in Birmingham.
OL,11,FThe challenges around equal pay, the
OL,12,FOracle system. I've been upfront about
OL,13,Fthat from the moment I became leader
OL,14,Fof the city council.
