OL,6,F"However, these issues haven't
OL,7,Fhappened in a vacuum. We are now
OL,8,Fseeing councils up and down the
OL,9,Fcountry facing the consequences of
OL,10,Fover a decades' worth of austerity and
OL,11,Freduced funding to local government.
OL,12,FIn Birmingham that means we've lost
OL,13,Fthe equivalent of #1billion.
